io.doov.tsparser

Class TypeScriptParserBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.tsparser.TypeScriptParserBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeScriptParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class TypeScriptParserBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypeScriptParserListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of TypeScriptParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
